text: John MacMurray (1958–2006) was a Canadian musician. John MacMurray or John Macmurray may also refer to: *John Van Antwerp MacMurray (1881–1960), American attorney and diplomat *John Macmurray (1891–1976), Scottish philosopher ==See also== *Webb Wilder, American musician, born John Webb McMurry
title: John MacMurray (disambiguation)
